title: BRIGADOON
description: Idyllic Southern Indiana Cabin Near Patoka Lake!

details.image01-description01: Let time stand still at this enchanting Taswell vacation rental near the Hoosier National Forest. Nestled on 87 acres, this 2-bedroom, 1-bath log cabin named the ‘Brigadoon Cabin’ invites families or friends seeking respite in nature. Soak in the sun while boating on Patoka Lake, or play numerous outdoor games within the White Oaks Cabins community. When you’re ready to retreat, sizzle up some dinner on the grill, dine in the private screened-in deck, and cozy up with a movie on the Smart TV.

title: TY-TANDDERWEN
description: Comfy Taswell Cabin Rental - Community Amenities!

details.image01-description01: Take solace in the simpler things in life at this Southern Indiana vacation rental near the Hoosier National Forest. Over 100 years young, this rustic Taswell studio named the ‘Ty-Tandderwen Cabin’ lets couples or small families reconnect with nature and one another. Start your mornings with coffee on the private porch, followed by an afternoon of fishing, hiking, and birdwatching. Come evening, return to the comforts of home, including a full bathroom, a Smart TV, and an electric stove!
